content: The Overwhelmed User: This archetype represents users who feel overwhelmed when interacting with the Cita Previa website, as expressed in the quote "The typography is awful and had me feeling a little overwhelmed, even if the information was simple." They may feel stressed by the process, and may need additional support or guidance to navigate the website. This archetype could include older users, users with disabilities, and users who are unfamiliar with technology. It could also include foreigners who may be unfamiliar with the website or who do not speak Spanish.
